# ffmpeg-core.wasm (30.7 MiB) must stay OUT of git: Cloudflare's CDN build
# (Pages or Workers assets, either CI) hard-fails any deploy containing a file
# over 25 MiB — that class of file froze alloflow-cdn.pages.dev 2026-07-03→05.
# This is the ROOT working copy of the same vendor tree as
# desktop/web-app/public/video_studio/vendor/ffmpeg/core/ (which carries the
# same scoped ignore). The file stays on local disk for mirror-sync and
# desktop/Firebase packaging, which deploy from the working tree.
# To restore on a fresh clone:
#   npm pack @ffmpeg/core@0.12.10 && extract package/dist/umd/ffmpeg-core.wasm here
ffmpeg-core.wasm
